Organization Name: MILLWOOD HOSPITAL | MENTAL HEALTH & CHEMICAL DEPENDENCY SERVICES
Description: A no-cost assessment is provided 24 hours a day for inpatient acute care as well as partial and intensive outpatient care for mental health and substance abuse.
